{"tid":287805,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"皇馬內部下季目標：雙殺巴塞，奪取六冠","createTime":"2017-06-17T16:56:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-17T18:21:04.000Z","uid":18279,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ff54e89c4db9c7e8808de9a7951e18f3204476d8","tid":287805,"uid":18279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T16:56:37.000Z","msg":"皇家馬德里於上季在未有對過前歐聯冠軍的情況奪得大耳杯令不少別隊球迷質疑，與14-15年巴塞先後打敗四大聯賽冠軍奪冠相比顯然含金量不足。但施丹帶領的皇馬今季先後殺退馬體會、祖雲達斯、拜仁套冠，明顯使批評者收聲。<br />\n<br />\n今年皇馬雖然是雙冠王，但對於皇馬董事會來說顯然是不完美，因為皇馬不但在魯營勉強靠拉莫斯戰和，更在主場落敗。最重要的是失落了國王盃，不能使死敵巴塞過一個無冠的賽季。<br />\n<br />\n對皇馬董事會而言，施丹雙冠王的成績十分耀眼，但對於下個賽季他們的要求卻不只如此，傳皇馬董事會內部將為施丹提供一切協助，斥資兩億元讓施丹在世界各地購入足球天才。而為了一個最大目的，是將巴塞徹底打敗，賽季上的兩戰不但要贏，還要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">四比零、五比零地贏</span>。在不同杯賽碰上巴塞亦要讓其俯首稱臣。<br />\n<br />\n皇馬董事會將打敗巴塞的目標與奪取另一次足球大滿貫並列，顯然是因為巴塞夢三時代給予皇馬極度的恥辱，多次的大挫令他們誓要將巴塞連根拔起，此後不再有能力與皇馬相持。<br />\n<br />\n而巴塞在今季更換主帥，華維迪是教父告魯夫和哥迪奧拿所認可的，但如今的巴塞面對巴塞青訓基因漸亡、中場駕馭力不再。華維迪如何改革值得注意。"},{"pid":"5b9d78961f6615ccb76d28df7c31186f491dd09a","tid":287805,"uid":993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T17:00:45.000Z","msg":"頭寒了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51eb6fab26440aaa6036dd73e50de7c26e489316","tid":287805,"uid":9708,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T17:03:41.000Z","msg":"單野來源都無 點俾疤狗save低下年抽水用啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65fafe9cae517b19dc23ce04199fbbd8637a87c4","tid":287805,"uid":17619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T17:10:03.000Z","msg":"炒鳩左拖舟咁啦咁都雙殺唔到巴"},{"pid":"8f80f15176de4f79bfaf8637657575adc70fd935","tid":287805,"uid":4574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T17:14:26.000Z","msg":"睇嚟當年5:0<br />\n嚇親皇馬 記足咁多年"},{"pid":"da93dc49d3968323fa9f1245f7b5a3225bd32d13","tid":287805,"uid":46151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T17:14:32.000Z","msg":"2億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n淨係用一個阿朗既價錢點456啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f057ef64a54073b0bdd66c931a9e8f3255d8ca19","tid":287805,"uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T18:17:03.000Z","msg":"無球證1冠都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deeda9db453bc0972fc7d31505d83e957ff7716c","tid":287805,"uid":54089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T18:19:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無球證1冠都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n緊係啦,無球證都開唔到波點贏冠軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"108d4cda9286a873babbd2019039bb2374054409","tid":287805,"uid":99861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T18:21:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>頭寒了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔關你鏝事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}